Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.54,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.04,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:12.38,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:18.55,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:25.31,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:31.73,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:38.16,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.58,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.92,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.92,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:00.18,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:06.52,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.73,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.94,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:19.70,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
